---
title: Zesty Jumbo Salmon Over Creamy Fresh Linguine with Dill and Roasted Brussels Sprouts
description: Bright and fresh flavours abound in this quick pasta dish accented with fresh dill and lemon zest. If you have chili flakes on hand, add a sprinkle over top for a bit of heat and colour.

